  "title": "Class 4 Driver (many OR) - East - WCDT",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></em></p><ul><li>Operate Class 4 vehicles to deliver and collect goods safely and on time</li><li>Load, unload, and secure cargo to prevent damage or loss</li><li>Conduct daily vehicle checks and report maintenance issues</li><li>Complete delivery documents and update delivery status accurately</li><li>Comply with traffic laws, safety standards, and company procedures</li></ul><p><br /><em><strong>Requirements:</strong></em></p><ul><li>Class 4 License is a must, with good driving record</li><li>Willing to work OT (1-2 hours per day, OT pay is provided).</li><li>Working Hours: 8.30am-5.30pm (Mon-Fri), 8.30am-12.30pm (Sat)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><br />Wecruit Pte Ltd | 20C0270<br />Tew Jie Wei | R22106822<br /></p>",
